---
title: PLT (Portobello, Lettuce and Tomato) with Tomato Relish, Pesto Aioli and Roasted Sweet Potato Wedges
description: You certainly won't miss the "B" in this ultra-satisfying PLT burger. Roasted Portobello adds umami depth, while slow-cooked tomato relish creates the perfect balance of sweet and savoury. Looking to make your sweet potato fries extra delicious? Any leftover pesto aioli makes a great dipping sauce (but you didn't hear that from us...)
